t-indent:23.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">专业优势：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">迎合了入世后我国市场经济对国际经济管理类复合型、应用型人才的迫切需求，专业适应面广，就业前景广阔。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">名校效应：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">东北师范大学为教育部直属、国内重点知名大学，在毕业证上副署盖章，并由东北师大对符合学位条件学员授予经济学学士学位，国家承认学历及学位。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">低成本高效率：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">学习时间短，大专学员可在学习期间直接参加本科段学习；同时拿双证，可在大专毕业同时获得大学本科文凭及学士学位。</span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:23.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">教师优势：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">专业课程由东北师范大学委派有多年教学经验的教师根据教学大纲进行重点串讲，辅助学员学习。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\">二、课程设置<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></strong></font></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none; margin-left: 6.75pt; margin-right: 6.75pt;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"left\" height=\"231\" width=\"989\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\">\r\n  <td style=\"width:55.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"74\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt;\r\n  mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-element:frame;mso-element-frame-hspace:9.0pt;\r\n  mso-element-wrap:around;mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-element-anchor-horizontal:\r\n  margin;mso-element-left:center;mso-element-top:3.05pt;mso-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">国家统考科目<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td style=\"width:378.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" width=\"504\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\n  mso-element:frame;mso-element-frame-hspace:9.0pt;mso-element-wrap:around;\r\n  mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-element-anchor-horizontal:margin;\r\n  mso-element-left:center;mso-element-top:3.05pt;mso-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color: black;\">中国近现代史纲要、马克思主义基本原理概论、<span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span>英语（二）、日语（二）、俄语（二）<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>三选一</span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1\" align=\"left\">\r\n  <td style=\"width:55.8pt;border:solid windowtext