\r\n  mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-element:frame;mso-element-frame-hspace:9.0pt;\r\n  mso-element-wrap:around;mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-element-anchor-horizontal:\r\n  margin;mso-element-left:center;mso-element-top:3.05pt;mso-height-rule:exactly\" align=\"center\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">加考科目<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td style=\"width:378.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:\r\n  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"504\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\n  mso-element:frame;mso-element-frame-hspace:9.0pt;mso-element-wrap:around;\r\n  mso-element-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-element-anchor-horizontal:margin;\r\n  mso-element-left:center;mso-element-top:3.05pt;mso-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"color: black;\">产业经济学、技术经济学、国际商务经济学概论（不考外语者加考三科）&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\"><br></span></strong></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\">三、招生对象<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></strong></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">专科升本：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">凡国民教育系列专科毕业生或在校专科生均可直接报考本科，专科毕业生可升本科；在读专科生符合条件可在专科毕业后获得大学本科文凭及学士学位（专本同读），为就业和考研做准备。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">本科二学历：</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">凡国民教育系列本科毕业生或在校本科生可直接报考本科，获得第二学历和第二学位，学习多专业知识，提高综合素质，拓展就业空间。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: black;\">四、学历说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></strong></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">根据省考委有关文件精神，考试成绩合格，实践环节考核合格，思想品德经鉴定符合要求者，由吉林省自考委颁发国际经济与管理专业本科毕业证书，主考学校东北师范大学在毕业证书上副署。符合学位授予条件者由东北师范大学授予经济学学士学位。毕业证及学位证由国家教育部统一进行电子注册，国家承认学历。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">毕业证认证条件<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">具有国民教育系列的专科毕业证书；各门课程成绩合格；毕业论文及格以上。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">学位证授予条件<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\">